Open wifi setting to the adapter you want to set up by right clicking on wifi button in status bar and selecting edit connections.
Go to IPv4 tab
Change to manual if not already.
Add the ip you want to use(local ip), i.e.:
ip: 192.168.2.42
netmask: 24
gateway: 192.168.2.1
dns servers: 192.168.2.1, 8.8.8.8, 8.8.4.4

Then restart computer.
